\u00e5 disse friomr\u00e5dene som en veldig meningsfull tilrettelegging for hundeeiere. Gran\u00e5sen er tidligere nevnt som et mulig omr\u00e5de, men vi har forel\u00f8pig ingen konkrete planer om \u00e5 etablere et nytt dressuromr\u00e5de, sier r\u00e5dgiver Helge Grenne i enheten for park- og friluftsliv i Trondheim kommune."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4adb04f73f970bbe38c8b0f0f17d2de68c7f62aa3e923050b4e71491864cf034"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-04-28T21:27:00.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Men det finnes noen steder for b\u00e5ndl\u00f8se hunder i Trondheim."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9437267.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sp407a29.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/bafc8e8c6dcc59a4b498b2713359a34652c6d6fc.jpg?598998c3"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["N\u00e5 m\u00e5 hunden i b\u00e5nd -adressa.no", "To friomr\u00e5der", "\u00d8nsker flere omr\u00e5der"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "bafc8e8c6dcc59a4b498b2713359a34652c6d6fc"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "pets"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["trondheim kommune", "hund", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["\u00f8stmarka", "kanonhaugen", "norsk kennel klub", "saupstad"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["morten haugen", "helge grenne"]}, {"field": "kw-tax